         <abstract id="aspace_43d3c446fe149488173fa2bc5dd44f82">The collection contains photographs documenting the construction and renovation of Berkeley College. Included are interior and exterior views of courtyards, the Fellow's suite, the dining hall, and architectural details. The collection also contains prints of architect's drawings and plans.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_ecd7fcd34acdd52be2f4c2133a14dcc5">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_e64ef5ac7fd9ed4812bb23fdc2c0d0d0">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Berkeley College, Yale University, Photographs (RU 603). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_9ba2e51c3ac71b0cbabb9ff391cdc263">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_3273f076dbbee5abc632c0754eacedde">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged in four series: I. Construction Progress Photographs, 1933-1934. II. General Views, 1934-1960. III. Oversize. IV. Slides and transparencies, and subsequent accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_62f5c4e0ed1b65ea05d2835aa998c7eb">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains photographs documenting the construction and renovation of Berkeley College. Included are interior and exterior views of courtyards, the Fellow's suite, the dining hall, and architectural details. The collection also contains prints of architect's drawings and plans.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
